This was my first Toker Poker that I bought and my last one that I’ve decorated. I need more Toker Pokers to Play with now. I wanted to make this one into a pendant that could be worn at a festival or while fishing or anywhere you don’t want to loose your lighter. It has a piece of Picture Jasper and a little Ivory Face that I thought Looked like a Moon 🌝 rising Over a landscape. And to hang the lighter I took a Paul Taylor leaf 🍂 Pendy from my collection and attached that to the bottom of the Toker Poker so that you can hang the lighter around your neck. I only attached half of the leaf to the lighter as I wanted to preserve Paul’s @paultaylorglass signature on the back side. This will also be a good test of the strength of the Sugru @sugru Moldable Glue that I’ve been using on these lighter covers. #tokerpoker #tokerpokerart #tokerpokerartistedition #mytokerpoker #sugru #sugruoriginal #mysugrufix #mysugru #paultaylorglass #headyart #headytokerpoker #tokerpokerlighter #tokerpokeradventures
